<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī śubha śaka
<lb n="2"/>varṣaṁbulu 1160
<lb n="3"/>viḷaṁbi saṁvatsa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ra Uttarāyaṇa saṁ
<lb n="5"/>krāṁti nimittaṁbu
<lb n="6"/>na svastiśrīmat [tā ?]
<lb n="7"/>[I] maṁḍalamulōni
<lb n="8"/>Eccuvāka śāsanulai
<lb n="9"/>na hermāṁḍi nāya
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kuṇi suputruṁḍu
<lb n="11"/>periya <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṁḍināya
<lb n="12" break="no"/>kuṁḍu tama tallida
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṁḍrulaku dharmārtha
<lb n="14"/>mugā dēśiyuyya
<lb n="15" break="no"/>goṁḍa paṭṭaṇaṁbai
<lb n="16" break="no"/>na mōṭṭupalli prasa
<lb n="17" break="no"/>nna kēśavadēvaraku
<lb n="18" break="no"/>nakhaṁḍa dīpamu
<lb n="19" break="no"/>na kiccina <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="20"/>lu 50 vīniṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="21"/>komarusvāmi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="22"/>muvāri ta<unclear>ma</unclear>
<lb n="23"/>dēvarāju nitya <unclear>māneṁ</unclear>
<lb n="24" break="no"/>ḍu nēyi naḍapaṁgala
<lb n="25"/>nāṁḍu putrānu pau
<lb n="26"/>trika mā caṁdratārā
<lb n="27"/>rkkamu 
